@Reasoning:
Verifies a non-trivial alphanumeric field name with a string value.
Catches a regression where the parser tokenizes "alice123" as
identifier + number rather than as a single string token (or where
the keys lookup is case-sensitive in the wrong direction).
@End Reasoning

@Implementation:
Increment total. Build `{"username": "alice123"}`. translate_mongodb_to_hir
with 0 arena. Branch on hir != 0; free source.
@End Implementation

@TestCases:
- Input `{"username": "alice123"}` -> non-null HIR, passed += 1
- Translator splits the value or returns 0 -> "Field translation: failed"
@End TestCases

